node.text:
The checkered flag is in the air at the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course as we bring home two top-five finishes!

@kylelarsonracin crossed the line in third, followed by @chaseelliott9 in fourth, @alex_bowman in 17th and @williambyron in 33rd.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 15, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
